//  Root cause:
//    newResourceGroup(capacity) computes bitmap_mask = (capacity >> 6) - 1
//    When capacity < 64: bitmap_mask = 0xFFFFFFFF (unsigned underflow)
//    The destructor iterates bitmap[0..bitmap_mask] on connection close,
